original_title: All Island Under 14 Rugby 10s to kick off tomorrow
original_body_lines: Sri Lanka Schools Rugby Football Association (SSRFA) conducted by All Island Dialog Elite Rugby tens will be worked off on May 27 (Zahira Maradana) and May 28 at the Royal Sports Complex.
In total 28 teams will lock horns in 8 groups in the event which will be minus Trinity College. By Shamseer Jaleel
